  "description": "A 36-card Petit Lenormand oracle by Yve Lepkowski (stolen-thyme.com), CC-BY-SA-4.0, with imagery drawn from the lyrics of Joanna Newsom. **A contemporary deck** — a cartomancy oracle, distinct from the tarot proper, so it sits apart from the historical tarot genealogy. A few card titles are her own (8 Cosmia for Coffin, 17 Goose for Stork, 22 Roads, 23 Rabbits, 30 Dove). 'The card' is her image text; 'Song reference' names the Newsom song (lyrics not reproduced); 'Traditional meaning' is the standard Lenormand reading. The two cards the earlier import had dropped (8 Cosmia, 9 Bouquet) are restored.",
